| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-3472 — Recovery Inhibition (arkana)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 4c4eca1e-e8e8-57d8-96e6-fbd2484a9990"
